WorkItem.Description:
I've been successfully using 2.2.19 and prior versions. With 2.2.20, I start from scratch.
 
I enter my character's details:
 
Name: Hoofee
Realm: Dath'Remar
Region: US
Race: Draenei
Class: Shaman
Model: Enhancement
 
I then choose Tools -> Reload Current Character From Armory
 
I then choose File -> Save As -> specify Hoofee.xml
 
Then I get a dialog box pop up with the error:
 
-----------------
Unhandled exception has occurred in your application. If you click Continue, the application will ignore this erro and attempt to continue. if you click Quit, the application will close immediately.
 
The was an error generating the XML document.
-----------------

----------------------
 
See the end of this message for details on invoking 
just-in-time (JIT) debugging instead of this dialog box.
